preibisch_imagelib2.img.cell

Interface Cells<A,C extends AbstractCell<A>>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    EuclideanSpace
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractCells, ListImgCells

    public interface Cells<A,C extends AbstractCell<A>>
extends EuclideanSpace
    An array of AbstractCells to store the data of a CellImg. Implementations may either keep all cells in memory, or cache them on demand.
    Author:
    ImgLib2 developers, Tobias Pietzsch
